description: Isis and Isabella Soprano square off for Playboy TV. SEXCETERA (Playboy cable TV) wanted to do a special on Ultimate Surrender, so over the course of one day we shot three matches. Due to lack of time this BONUS EXTRA UPDATE was rushed. We only had time for three 4 minutes rounds, however we got in a full round 4. Have a nice weekend.
title: AN UN-SANCTIONED US MATCH
